included.description: I'm a social psychologist on the Compassion team at Facebook, where our mission is to support people through sensitive life experiences and promote well-being. I'm particularly interested in the impact of technology on people's well-being, and as a quantitative researcher I use a variety of methods to measure and understand people's experience both online and offline (e.g., survey design and analysis, experiments, machine learning, log data analysis). I also work with fellow researchers, data scientists, product managers, designers, and engineers to translate research insights into products/decisions aimed to provide support and promote well-being.
